_sText:
Hello everybody.
I made another ZE map.
The map has:
• 64 spawns
• 5 levels + ZM round(6 level)
• 6 items for humans
Item 1: Heal staff
Item 2: Tornado staff
Item 3: Freeze staff
Item 4: Earth staff
Item 5: Fire staff
Item 6: Ultimate staff(2, 3, 4, 5, 6 level)

• 5 items for zombies
Item 1: Cromcruach(4, 5 level)
Item 2: Glasgavelen(3, 4, 5 level)
Item 3: Fire
Item 4: Gravity
Item 5: Freeze

• 3 bosses
